data.description: Newly remodeled 3rd level condo with new kitchen, new bathroom and renovated fireplace. Refinished hard wood floors and new paint in all rooms. Vaulted ceilings. Large arched windows with ample natural light. Mountain views from patio, dining space and master bedroom. Washer/ dryer hookup. Air conditioner. Garage and separate outdoor parking space. Community pool.
